<h2>Cyber Space Stages</h2>

The Beta Edition includes <strong>7 stages numbered 1-1 through 1-7</strong>, each with multiple routes that vary in difficulty. The level design pulls from across the Sonic franchise: Stage 1-2 and 1-3 channel <strong>Water Palace</strong> from Sonic Rush with gorgeous aquatic environments. Stage 1-4 shifts to a <strong>Chemical Plant</strong>-style industrial aesthetic. Stage 1-7, the final level, is widely considered the highlight — a 2D interpretation of Frontiers' Starfall that many players feel outdoes the source material.

Level gimmicks keep each stage feeling distinct: <strong>rail grinding, crystal light switches, fish circle launchers, rainbow rings, and moving platforms</strong> all force you to adapt your approach. A dual ranking system scores you on both time and ring collection separately, with grades from D up to S-rank and Diamond, plus Bronze/Silver/Gold medals — giving completionists plenty to chase.

